## 安装

```reStructuredText
npm install --save axios vue-axios
```

## 引入

```vue
import Vue from 'vue'
import axios from 'axios'
import VueAxios from 'vue-axios'

axios.defaults.baseURL='http://localhost:8000';  // 可以设置baseURL
Vue.use(VueAxios, axios)
```

